roximately $400.0 million. ##TABLE_END##TABLE_START &#9679; In August, we closed the acquisition of 61.1% indirect controlling interest in Teraco, a leading carrier-neutral colocation provider in South Africa, for total cash consideration of $1.7 billion in a transaction valuing Teraco at approximately $3.3 billion. ##TABLE_END##TABLE_START &#9679; In August, we sold a non-core building in Dallas for net proceeds of $203 million resulting in a net gain on sale of $174 million. ##TABLE_END##TABLE_START &#9679; In August, we entered into a term loan agreement, comprised of a &#8364;375.0 million three-year senior unsecured term loan facility and a &#8364;375.0 million five-year senior unsecured term loan facility. The term loans were funded in August (&#8364;500.0 million) and in September (&#8364;250.0 million). The interest rate for borrowings under the term loans is based on EURIBO, plus a margin based on the corporate credit rating of our long-term senior unsecured debt. ##TABLE_END

